QuestData.Title: A Worthy Challenge: Raigonn
QuestData.Description: $n, I need you to assemble a cracking group and lead them into the Gate of the Setting Sun. Activate the Challenger's Orb therein and lay waste to Raigonn.$B$BReturn to me when you've completed this challenge, and I shall reward you handsomely.
QuestData.LogDescription: Complete the Gate of the Setting Sun Challenge Mode.
